HEADWORD: Probang
<hw>Pro"bang</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Probe</er>.]</ety> <def>A slender elastic rod, as of whalebone, with
a sponge on the end, for removing obstructions from the esophagus,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

